对他们的控告都来自竞争对手
the allegations come from the competition.

1260
01:35:37,390 --> 01:35:39,020
竞标失败了  心里不舒服
Outbid. Bitter.

1261
01:35:39,560 --> 01:35:41,060
比如说奥赖恩・阿彻
Like Oline Archer.

1262
01:35:41,560 --> 01:35:44,980
也可能是乐班德尔买通了一些重要官员呢
Or maybe Lebendauer has the cooperation of key officials.

1263
01:35:45,070 --> 01:35:48,030
也许买通的这些还不管用
And maybe when that cooperation isn't enough,

1264
01:35:48,410 --> 01:35:51,660
所以就杀了收买不到的人  比如奥赖恩・阿彻
they kill people who won't be bought off. Like Oline Archer.

1265
01:35:51,740 --> 01:35:53,910
海伦  这些东西你真的相信吗
Helen, how much of this do you honestly believe?

1266
01:35:54,040 --> 01:35:56,200
我信不信不重要
