It doesn't even matter how much I can prove.

1268
01:35:58,920 --> 01:36:01,420
唯一重要的是有多少是真的
It only matters how much is true.

1269
01:36:01,710 --> 01:36:03,710
你知道自己听起来有多可笑吗
Do you know how delusional you sound?

1270
01:36:04,210 --> 01:36:05,880
你怎么回事
What happened to you?

1271
01:36:06,260 --> 01:36:09,690
你就这么想要这个人死掉
Are you really so set on putting this man to death

1272
01:36:09,690 --> 01:36:10,430
甚至不顾
