1274
01:36:25,940 --> 01:36:27,780
如果杰克・雷彻是对的
If Jack Reacher's right,

1275
01:36:28,280 --> 01:36:31,610
我的性命  你女儿的性命
my life, your daughter's life,

1276
01:36:32,280 --> 01:36:34,120
现在岌岌可危
is in danger now.

1277
01:36:35,790 --> 01:36:37,790
我的命运全由你决定
Whatever happens to me next is on your head,

1278
01:36:38,250 --> 01:36:40,210
无论是不是与你有关
whether you're involved or not.

1279
01:36:42,960 --> 01:36:44,180
你是地区检察官
You are the District Attorney

1280
01:36:44,180 --> 01:36:47,050
我也向你提供了有力证据
and I've given you compelling evidence

1281
01:36:47,130 --> 01:36:49,050
来调查乐班德尔公司
to investigate Lebendauer Enterprises.

1282
01:36:49,470 --> 01:36:53,300
你的下一步会告诉我你到底站在哪边
Your next move will tell me which side you're on.

1283
01:36:56,140 --> 01:36:57,600
我明白了  这是个考验
I see. It's a test.

1284
