1291
01:37:28,340 --> 01:37:30,260
如果你真的被收买了  我又能有多安全
And how safe will I be if you're part of it?

1292
01:37:30,670 --> 01:37:32,300
天哪  海伦
Jesus, Helen.

1293
01:38:33,400 --> 01:38:35,030
开会吗  还是私事
Business meeting or personal?

1294
01:38:35,240 --> 01:38:37,240
两者都有
Hard to tell them apart.

1295
01:38:37,700 --> 01:38:39,070
我想也是
I'll bet.

1296
