海伦吗
Helen?

1297
01:39:42,560 --> 01:39:43,560
不是
No.

1298
01:39:45,270 --> 01:39:46,600
对不起打错了
Sorry, wrong number.

1299
01:39:46,930 --> 01:39:48,560
你是雷彻吗
Is this Reacher?

1300
01:39:50,940 --> 01:39:52,060
你是谁
Who is this?

1301
01:39:55,280 --> 01:39:57,610
你是雷彻吗
Is this Reacher?

1302
01:40:02,450 --> 01:40:05,580
是你  跟踪我的那个人
It's you. The guy from the car.

1303
01:40:08,080 --> 01:40:09,290
你男朋友打来的
It's your boyfriend.

1304
01:40:11,130 --> 01:40:12,460
雷彻  是你吗
Reacher, is it you?

1305
01:40:14,090 --> 01:40:15,090
海伦  你受伤了吗
Helen, are you hurt?

1306
01:40:15,300 --> 01:40:17,260
如果你不在一小时内过来的话她就会受伤
Well, she's gonna be if you're not here in one hour.

1307
01:40:18,090 --> 01:40:20,130
要我告诉你怎么做吗
Do I have to tell you how this works?

1308
01:40:20,260 --> 01:40:22,050
你们会让我绕几圈确认没人跟着
You'll bounce me around to make sure I'm not followed,

1309
01:40:22,140 --> 01:40:24,600
然后走进你们的陷阱再杀了我
then walk me into an ambush and kill me.

1310
01:40:24,810 --> 01:40:26,970
你把惊喜都毁了
Aw, you ruined my surprise.

1311
01:40:27,270 --> 01:40:28,930
我有个更好的办法
Well, I can do one better.

1312
01:40:29,440 --> 01:40:31,650
我去了亨吉溪镇的射击场
I went down to the gun range at Hinge Creek.

1313
01:40:32,270 --> 01:40:34,090
我拿到了录像  指纹
I got the picture, prints,

1314
01:40:34,090 --> 01:40:35,610
我会去找联邦政府的人
and I'm going to the Feds.

1315
01:40:35,780 --> 01:40:37,440
那个律师随你处置
The lawyer's all yours.

1316
01:40:41,950 --> 01:40:42,990
把柴克找来
Get the Zec.

1317
01:40:52,460 --> 01:40:54,500
我又想了一下  还是把你杀了好
On second thought, I'd like to kill you.

1318
01:40:54,790 --> 01:40:56,210
那我们就胜者全得吧
Let's say winner take all.

1319
01:40:56,300 --> 01:40:57,340
听着  臭小子
Listen to me, you prick.

1320
01:40:57,460 --> 01:40:59,130
如果你一小时之内不来的话我就把这个婊子杀
I will kill this bitch if you're not here in one...

1321
01:41:00,840 --> 01:41:02,130
妈的
Shit!

1322
01:41:08,520 --> 01:41:10,140
你以为我是个英雄吗
You think I'm a hero?

1323
01:41:10,350 --> 01:41:14,190
我不是英雄  我是个一无所有的流浪者
I am not a hero. I'm a drifter with nothing to lose.

1324
01:41:14,520 --> 01:41:17,360
如果你杀了那姑娘来陷害我
You killed that girl to put me in a frame.

1325
01:41:17,480 --> 01:41:21,490
我扒光你的皮
I mean to beat you to death and drink your blood from a boot.

1326
01:41:22,360 --> 01:41:24,310
听着  按我说的做
Now, this is how it's going to work.

1327
01:41:24,310 --> 01:41:26,030
你把地址给我
You're gonna give me the address

1328
01:41:26,200 --> 01:41:28,620
我他妈什么时候准备好了就过来
and I'll be along when I am damn good and ready.

1329
01:41:28,700 --> 01:41:30,950
如果我打过来不是她接的
If she doesn't answer the phone when I call this number,

1330
01:41:31,040 --> 01:41:32,870
只要我觉得她受伤了
if I even think you've hurt her,

1331
01:41:33,210 --> 01:41:34,710
我会立刻消失
I disappear.

1332
01:41:34,830 --> 01:41:37,480
如果你够聪明的话  我不是威胁你
And if you're smart, that scares you,

1333
01:41:37,480 --> 01:41:39,630
你们在明我在暗
because I'm in your blind spot

1334
01:41:39,710 --> 01:41:41,840
而且我没什么别的可做
and I have nothing better to do.

1335
01:41:50,060 --> 01:41:51,100
你有笔吗
You got a pen?

1336
01:41:53,230 --> 01:41:54,560
不需要
Don't need one.

1337
01:42:58,960 --> 01:43:00,770
要是每次被大兵找来帮忙
If I had a dollar for every

1338
01:43:00,780 --> 01:43:03,460
我都收一美元就好了
time the Army called the Corps for help.

1339
01:43:05,800 --> 01:43:07,630
-给我带家伙了吗  -带了
-You have something for me? -Yeah.

1340
01:43:08,300 --> 01:43:09,760
给你
Here.

1341
01:43:14,270 --> 01:43:15,310
你在开玩笑吧
You're kidding, right?

1342
01:43:15,430 --> 01:43:16,890
我十年前看过你射击
Just because I saw you shoot ten years ago

1343
01:43:16,980 --> 01:43:20,440
并不代表我就允许你用我的枪杀人
doesn't mean I'll let you kill some asshole with my gun.

1344
01:43:20,650 --> 01:43:22,320
我说了这事很严重
I told you how serious this was.

1345
01:43:22,650 --> 01:43:24,320
我也来了  对吧
And I showed up, didn't I?

1346
01:43:25,150 --> 01:43:26,320
那就开始吧
So let's get to it.

1347
01:43:28,280 --> 01:43:29,320
你的对手应该
Now, your shooter will be

1348
01:43:29,820 --> 01:43:32,910
就在这些灯后  明白吗
right up there behind those lights. Okay?

1349
01:43:32,990 --> 01:43:35,950
他能看到来去两边的所有情况
He can cover both roads coming and going.

1350
01:43:36,460 --> 01:43:39,830
你一站起来就能将你击中
And kill you just as soon as you stand up.

1351
01:43:39,960 --> 01:43:41,130
那你能把他引出来吗
Well, can you take him out?

1352
01:43:41,670 --> 01:43:42,960
共进晚餐吗
What, to dinner you mean?

1353
01:43:45,010 --> 01:43:46,590
听着  我不知道你平时
Look, I don't know the type

1354
01:43:46,590 --> 01:43:49,340
都跟什么人打交道  雷彻
of people you normally associate with, Reacher.

1355
01:43:49,680 --> 01:43:51,500
不过我不习惯
But I'm not in the habit of

1356
01:43:51,500 --> 01:43:54,680
你一声令下就开车到郊外
driving out to the boonies at the drop of a hat

1357
01:43:55,140 --> 01:43:58,480
然后随便放倒一些陌生人好吗
and just picking off some total strangers, all right?

1358
01:43:59,350 --> 01:44:01,030
总之  我什么都看不到
Anyway, I can't see anything,

1359
01:44:01,030 --> 01:44:02,190
