not with them lights up.

1360
01:44:02,320 --> 01:44:03,860
那把它们打灭
So shoot them out.

1361
01:44:04,650 --> 01:44:07,360
当然好  这样他们就知道我的位置了
Yeah, sure. And then he knows right where I am.

1362
01:44:07,490 --> 01:44:09,490
我还不如引火自焚呢
I might as well set myself on fire.

1363
01:44:10,530 --> 01:44:13,370
不对  先生  他们开枪了我再开枪
No, sir. I'll start shooting when he does.

1364
01:44:16,040 --> 01:44:18,160
那你说怎么让他们先开枪
And how do you propose we get him started?

1365
01:44:18,710 --> 01:44:22,540
你可以开跑啊
Well, you could always start running.

1366
01:44:30,010 --> 01:44:31,550
你眼睛怎么了
What's wrong with your eye?

1367
