Hey, Gunny, you mind if I ask you kind of a personal question?

1369
01:44:40,690 --> 01:44:42,520
怎么  你觉得我不会射击了吗
What, you don't think I can shoot any more?

1370
01:44:43,230 --> 01:44:44,860
这技能不练就没了
It is a perishable skill.

1371
01:44:45,730 --> 01:44:47,070
对  没错
Yeah, well,

1372
01:44:47,650 --> 01:44:49,740
还有一小时太阳就出来了
the sun will be up in an hour.

1373
01:44:51,240 --> 01:44:52,570
我们动手吧
Let's get going.

1374
01:45:09,590 --> 01:45:11,760
我听到他们管你叫柴克
I heard them call you the Zec.

1375
01:45:12,550 --> 01:45:13,890
意思是囚犯
That means "Prisoner."

1376
01:45:15,760 --> 01:45:16,930
对吗
Yes?

1377
01:45:19,850 --> 01:45:21,270
告诉我  你杀了这么多人
Tell me, killing all those people,

1378
01:45:22,020 --> 01:45:23,520
我只能认为你挣的钱
I have to believe the money you're making

1379
01:45:23,600 --> 01:45:25,020
不可能足够
can't possibly be enough to just...

1380
